still press charges!


776
00:54:48.276 --> 00:54:50.345
What has this man told--

777
00:54:50.378 --> 00:54:52.779
- Get off of me!
- Shut the fuck up, hey!


778
00:54:52.813 --> 00:54:54.115
- Get off of me!
- Shut up!


779
00:54:54.148 --> 00:54:55.749
Dad, stop!

780
00:54:59.920 --> 00:55:02.789
Don't hurt him.
I'm okay.


781
00:55:04.891 --> 00:55:05.960
So, what?

782
00:55:05.994 --> 00:55:07.962
You're a daddy figure now?

783
00:55:20.874 --> 00:55:22.443
Does he know?

784
00:55:22.477 --> 00:55:23.544
No.

785
00:55:25.313 --> 00:55:27.382
You never lose, do you?

786
00:55:27.415 --> 00:55:29.417
