791
00:55:43.197 --> 00:55:44.565
And your back foot
should pivot.


792
00:55:45.566 --> 00:55:47.035
That's right.
Okay.


793
00:55:47.068 --> 00:55:48.869
Now, full motion
should look like this.


794
00:55:51.205 --> 00:55:53.207
- Hey, Ave.
- "Ave?"


795
00:55:53.241 --> 00:55:55.143
Dylan just wanted me
to help him with his swing.


796
00:55:55.977 --> 00:55:57.078
Um...

797
00:55:57.944 --> 00:56:00.214
can I talk
to you outside for a sec?


798
00:56:02.083 --> 00:56:03.151
Sure.

799
00:56:04.918 --> 00:56:06.387
Here.
All right, line it up.


800
00:56:06.421 --> 00:56:07.488
Okay?
I'll be right back.


801
00:56:17.565 --> 00:56:19.300
What's up?

802
00:56:19.334 --> 00:56:20.401
Um...

803
00:56:21.669 --> 00:56:23.338
Dylan called me
"Dad" today.


804
00:56:25.273 --> 00:56:26.341
What?

805
00:56:27.041 --> 00:56:28.109
What?

806
00:56:32.080 --> 00:56:34.048
I-- I don't know
how to respond to that.


807
00:56:34.082 --> 00:56:35.249
What do you mean?

808
00:56:37.618 --> 00:56:39.153
He thinks
you're his dad, David.


809
00:56:39.187 --> 00:56:40.421
Ever since
you showed up.


810
00:56:41.489 --> 00:56:45.560
I don't know if it's some
sense he believes he has.


811
00:56:45.593 --> 00:56:47.962
It's why he wants
to see you all the time.


812
00:56:49.664 --> 00:56:51.199
He's curious.

813
00:56:53.501 --> 00:56:55.902
Just don't--
don't bring this up with him


814
00:56:55.936 --> 00:56:58.172
and hopefully
he will just forget about it.


815
00:57:01.309 --> 00:57:03.378
I cannot deal
with this right now.


816
00:57:03.411 --> 00:57:04.579
Well, I can.

817
00:57:07.014 --> 00:57:08.882
I can be there for him.

818
00:57:09.484 --> 00:57:10.651
For you. I--

819
00:57:12.086 --> 00:57:13.521
I can be
that person.


820
00:57:21.362 --> 00:57:22.563
Good night, David.

821
00:57:39.447 --> 00:57:41.215
Strike three!
Batter, out.


822
00:57:42.116 --> 00:57:43.184
Switch sides.

823
00:58:05.206 --> 00:58:07.575
Excuse me, are you going
to keep calling the game?


824
00:58:07.608 --> 00:58:08.942
Are you
who I think you are?


825
00:58:09.577 --> 00:58:11.712
-Sorry?
-Are you who I think you are?


826
00:58:15.450 --> 00:58:17.485
-Let's go, buddy!
-Go Dylan.


827
00:58:21.456 --> 00:58:23.257
Oh, that's okay, buddy.
That's okay.


828
00:58:23.291 --> 00:58:25.126
Right back here.
Right back.


829
00:58:25.159 --> 00:58:27.028
Hey.

830
00:58:27.061 --> 00:58:28.729
Aren't you that guy who killed
that dude in a car accident?


831
00:58:28.763 --> 00:58:31.466
- Oh, yeah, yeah.
- Oh yeah, it is you.


832
00:58:31.499 --> 00:58:32.967
How the hell
did you get this job?


833
00:58:33.434 --> 00:58:35.036
Ma'am, it's a--
it's a minimum wage--


834
00:58:35.069 --> 00:58:36.504
I don't care.

835
00:58:36.537 --> 00:58:38.739
You shouldn't be
umping a kid's baseball game.


836
00:58:40.041 --> 00:58:41.742
Who hired you?

837
00:58:41.776 --> 00:58:43.544
Oh dude, my dad read about you
in the paper a few weeks ago.


838
00:58:43.578 --> 00:58:45.546
You-- you must have
just gotten out.


839
00:58:46.347 --> 00:58:47.515
Dude, you're a monster.

840
00:58:50.251 --> 00:58:52.186
I'm going to call
the commissioner.


841
00:58:52.220 --> 00:58:54.255
Hell,
maybe even the Free Press.


842
00:58:55.289 --> 00:58:56.357
Ava.

843
00:58:57.825 --> 00:58:59.427
-Hey.
-It's okay.


844
00:58:59.861 --> 00:59:01.329
David,
I'm not mad at you.


845
00:59:01.362 --> 00:59:02.630
It's just the kids.
I'm sorry.


846
00:59:02.663 --> 00:59:05.299
I just need time.
I just need space.


847
00:59:07.368 --> 00:59:08.769
Watch the game
and then we'll go.


848
00:59:11.672 --> 00:59:12.773
Yeah.

849
00:59:25.820 --> 00:59:28.022
Listen, kid.

850
00:59:28.823 --> 00:59:30.191
I don't want to do this.

851
00:59:31.425 --> 00:59:32.660
But some parents
around the league


852
00:59:32.693 --> 00:59:34.262
