853
00:59:35.530 --> 00:59:39.166
I told you
not to take the mask off.


854
00:59:46.140 --> 00:59:47.174
Listen.

855
00:59:47.842 --> 00:59:49.544
Umping
wasn't for you anyways.


856
00:59:50.745 --> 00:59:52.179
Take the rest
of the season off.


857
00:59:52.213 --> 00:59:53.614
We can talk about
a coaching job


858
00:59:53.648 --> 00:59:54.715
later in the year.

859
00:59:55.750 --> 00:59:57.118
When you're out
of the news more.


860
00:59:57.151 --> 00:59:58.219
Okay?

