01:00:01.289 --> 01:00:03.291
Things like this die down
quicker than you'd think.


862
01:00:05.126 --> 01:00:07.395
There's going to be a bigger
and worse story next week.


863
01:00:13.768 --> 01:00:15.102
Hey.

864
01:00:15.136 --> 01:00:16.203
Head up.

865
01:00:17.772 --> 01:00:19.540
Don't let this
beat you down, kid.


866
01:00:20.908 --> 01:00:22.843
You made a mistake.

867
01:00:22.877 --> 01:00:24.145
Make up for it.

868
01:00:25.613 --> 01:00:27.248
That's the best
you can do.


869
01:00:31.886 --> 01:00:33.154
Coming!

870
01:00:42.763 --> 01:00:45.399
-What are you doing here?
-Let's go. Come on.


871
01:00:45.433 --> 01:00:47.201
-Where?
-Coming or what?


872
01:00:47.935 --> 01:00:49.370
Come on,
I'll tell you on the way.


873
01:00:50.705 --> 01:00:51.772
'Kay, just--

874
01:00:55.776 --> 01:00:57.478
Okay, honey,

875
01:00:57.511 --> 01:00:59.180
I'm going to go out
with David for a little bit.


876
01:00:59.213 --> 01:01:00.748
I'll be
back soon, okay?


877
01:01:00.781 --> 01:01:02.683
Can I watch the game,
please?


878
01:01:02.717 --> 01:01:04.518
Mmm,
what do I say?


879
01:01:04.552 --> 01:01:06.253
Only if I
watch the news.


880
01:01:06.287 --> 01:01:07.655
Good boy.
I love you.


881
01:01:07.688 --> 01:01:08.856
Muah! Muah.

882
01:01:09.690 --> 01:01:11.192
Be good.

883
01:01:11.859 --> 01:01:13.861
I'll have Jessica
come check on you.


884
01:01:13.894 --> 01:01:15.429
Love you, sweetie.

