01:04:11.072 --> 01:04:12.640
Yeah.
Just give me a sec.


928
01:04:13.774 --> 01:04:14.842
Okay.

929
01:04:54.481 --> 01:04:56.117
Mom!

930
01:05:02.923 --> 01:05:04.692
Why didn't you tell me?

931
01:05:10.098 --> 01:05:12.833
I know who Mister really is!

932
01:05:12.867 --> 01:05:14.970
The lady
on the news told me!


933
01:05:17.638 --> 01:05:19.406
You betrayed me!

934
01:05:20.008 --> 01:05:21.876
I hate you,
I hate you, I hate you!


935
01:05:21.909 --> 01:05:22.978
What happened?

936
01:05:23.011 --> 01:05:24.678
You lied to me!

937
01:05:40.661 --> 01:05:42.496
- David.
- Don't come near me.


938
01:05:42.529 --> 01:05:44.065
-I fucking mean it.
-I just want to talk.


939
01:05:44.099 --> 01:05:45.633
