don't fucking touch me!


940
01:05:45.666 --> 01:05:47.969
All I'm asking for
is a conversation.


941
01:05:48.003 --> 01:05:49.137
A second chance.

942
01:05:51.206 --> 01:05:52.840
You want
a second chance, huh?


943
01:05:52.873 --> 01:05:54.942
Yes. Please.

944
01:05:55.576 --> 01:05:56.644
Okay.

945
01:05:57.245 --> 01:05:58.512
All right.

946
01:05:59.947 --> 01:06:01.916
Go home.

947
01:06:01.949 --> 01:06:04.652
Go home or wherever
the fuck you came from.


948
01:06:06.021 --> 01:06:07.721
Build yourself
a time machine.


949
01:06:07.755 --> 01:06:08.923
Are you with me so far?

950
01:06:11.558 --> 01:06:13.028
Go back in time, okay?

951
01:06:13.061 --> 01:06:14.662
Don't beat my mother.

952
01:06:14.695 --> 01:06:16.064
Don't beat my brother.

953
01:06:16.097 --> 01:06:17.798
Don't come home
drunk every night.


954
01:06:19.733 --> 01:06:20.801
Can you do that?

955
01:06:21.602 --> 01:06:23.204
I know I can't
change the past, David.


956
01:06:23.238 --> 01:06:24.738
Yeah,
you're goddamn right you can't.


957
01:06:25.739 --> 01:06:26.807
David.

958
01:06:30.045 --> 01:06:31.112
David, please.

959
01:06:34.515 --> 01:06:35.582
David.

960
01:06:36.084 --> 01:06:37.218
David,
if you can hear me...


961
01:06:38.186 --> 01:06:39.720
Jackson is in jail.

962
01:06:42.523 --> 01:06:43.857
He got into a fight
in a bar,


963
01:06:43.891 --> 01:06:45.492
and he called me
to bail him out.


964
01:06:45.526 --> 01:06:46.627
But...

965
01:06:47.728 --> 01:06:48.796
I think
it should be you.


966
01:06:51.199 --> 01:06:53.101
I think you should
be the one to go get him.


967
01:07:34.608 --> 01:07:35.676
You all right?

968
01:07:45.020 --> 01:07:46.287
Hey!

969
01:07:46.321 --> 01:07:47.755
Thanks for the bailout, bro.

970
01:07:47.788 --> 01:07:49.523
Wouldn't be
the first time.


971
01:07:49.991 --> 01:07:51.026
Is that
what this is about?


972
01:07:51.558 --> 01:07:52.826
Is this about what?

973
01:07:55.263 --> 01:07:56.530
It is, isn't it?

974
01:07:57.731 --> 01:07:59.134
You're still mad
about what I did.


975
01:08:00.301 --> 01:08:02.736
Do you know
who I did it for?


976
01:08:02.770 --> 01:08:04.905
-I did it for you, Jackson.
-See, there.


977
01:08:04.938 --> 01:08:06.975
That's the problem
right there.


978
01:08:07.008 --> 01:08:08.609
Sure, yeah,
you went to prison for it.


979
01:08:08.642 --> 01:08:09.743
For me.

980
01:08:09.777 --> 01:08:11.578
Thank you,
Master David.


981
01:08:11.612 --> 01:08:12.880
Thank you
for taking the fall.


982
01:08:12.913 --> 01:08:15.682
I owe you my life.
But fuck you!


983
01:08:15.716 --> 01:08:17.751
You caused that accident
way more than I did.


984
01:08:17.785 --> 01:08:19.087
And then
you take the fall


985
01:08:19.120 --> 01:08:20.888
and think
you're baptized or something?


986
01:08:20.921 --> 01:08:21.889
I didn't cause the accident.
You drove the car.


987
01:08:21.922 --> 01:08:23.324
You took me to the bar!

988
01:08:23.358 --> 01:08:25.926
We took your car.
You chose to drink.


989
01:08:25.960 --> 01:08:27.828
You chose
to make me drive home.


990
01:08:29.364 --> 01:08:31.565
I was 18.
How is that fair?


991
01:08:33.767 --> 01:08:35.236
You're not the angel
you think you are.


992
01:08:35.270 --> 01:08:37.105
I don't think that.
I didn't say that.


993
01:08:38.073 --> 01:08:39.606
Well,
that's what Mom thought.


994
01:08:40.308 --> 01:08:42.243
Don't you dare
bring mom into this.


995
01:08:42.277 --> 01:08:43.777
You're the oldest.

996
01:08:43.811 --> 01:08:45.879
The athletic one.
The good-looking one.


997
01:08:46.514 --> 01:08:49.284
The perfect son that saved us
from our abusive father.


998
01:08:49.317 --> 01:08:51.986
Me, I'm the runt
she never gave two shits about.


999
01:08:52.420 --> 01:08:53.988
She'd look at me
and feel like a failure.


1000
01:08:54.022 --> 01:08:55.656
-Jackson!
-No, you listen.


1001
01:08:55.689 --> 01:08:57.825
That's all she said,
all the time.


1002
01:08:57.858 --> 01:08:59.227
You're perfect
and I'm not.


1003
01:08:59.260 --> 01:09:00.727
You saved me.

1004
01:09:00.761 --> 01:09:02.130
And I should have been
the one in jail.


1005
01:09:02.163 --> 01:09:03.231
Not you. Me.

1006
01:09:05.732 --> 01:09:07.268
She couldn't even
look me in the eye anymore.


1007
01:09:08.069 --> 01:09:09.137
Jack...

1008
01:09:11.772 --> 01:09:13.007
What,
you want me to apologize?


1009
01:09:13.041 --> 01:09:14.075
I killed someone!

1010
