01:09:25.153 --> 01:09:27.288
I didn't ask for it.

1013
01:09:28.789 --> 01:09:30.924
I didn't ask
for you to take the fall.


1014
01:09:32.260 --> 01:09:34.828
I've been suffering
for five fucking years.


1015
